data.title: Phi Sigma Pi National Honor Fraternity
data.text:
Phi Sigma Pi wants to come to your campus!

We are currently looking to expand to the following campuses. Don't see your campus? You can learn more about starting a Chapter here.

Steps to Starting a Chapter

Phi Sigma Pi Membership is designed as a three-part approach for starting a Chapter on your campus. The steps for establishing a Chapter are;

Individuals on your campus complete the Membership Program,

Students expressing interest and who have completed the program will work alongside the National Office and other campus Members to prepare a petition,

Petition the school for recognition.
